Package fr.ensimag.deca.syntax

Lexical and syntaxctic analysis for the Deca language.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractDecaLexer
    This is the super class for the lexer.
    AbstractDecaParser
    The super class of the generated parser.
    CircularInclude
    Exception raised when a chain of #include is circular, i.e. a file includes a file which has already been included.
    DecacErrorListner
    Error listener that stops the compilation at the first error usuing ParseCancellationException.
    IncludeFileNotFound
    Exception raised when a #include is found for a file that cannot be found or opened.
    InvalidLValue
    Syntax error for an expression that should be an lvalue (ie that can be assigned), but is not.
